{"type": "article", "id": 8908, "title": "KAZbrella 新一代雨伞", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-27T07:16:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235246Y7QxScVh81fi6Rg0.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t雨伞为我们带来便捷，但用过后，水滴滴答答也一直是困扰着我们的一个问题。有人设计了雨伞托，来接住留下来的水，而设计师 Jenan Kazim 则从雨伞的形态入手，直接把雨伞与水接触的那一面折到了里面。这个叫做 “KAZbrella” 的伞打开后和普通的雨伞并无二致，但它的打开和收起的方向却和普通的雨伞正好相反。这样一来，既解决了雨水打湿地板的问题，又解决了进出车门等狭窄空间收伞的问题以及在人群中撑伞的问题。<a href=\"http://www.kazbrella.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235244u87WfIRi0Fx1mv4B.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.79487179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235244FK3N4EABnewV5mRa.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.81623932\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235245kIvgyrM0x46st9eT.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.7991453\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235245BHb4vu1ejRmEZTLA.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}